text:
Staff is quite helpful while in the shop. Do take note that although the phone number is correct, they do not pick up the phone at all. Verified the number with them, and tried calling while in the shop.

Saturday hours says until 1230, but they will close at 12pm.
This is a retail pharmacy with no pharmacist on duty and no prescription medication available. Staffs are friendly and approachable.
Sat open 8.30 to 12.30 pm but website says closed. Staff not answering phone on Saturday
The cashier was jumpy . Only a lady customer ahead of me . He was in a bad mood . I told him no need to be so jumpy . He kept quiet . How to serve customers . ? No courtesy n friendly cashier
Very friendly staff. It does not open on Sundays and Public Holidays. Nearest parking is at 332 Anchorvale Link, Singapore 541332.
